// Dotted path ends with '.' and nothing follows at all (@firescript/ form).
// Kept in its own file (rather than folded into import_syntax_errors.fire):
// combining this with other malformed-import cases in one file caused an
// earlier case's error recovery to leave stray token-stream state that
// prevented the "nothing follows the trailing dot" branch in
// firescript/parser/declarations.py (_parse_import) from actually being
// exercised, even though the diagnostic still matched by a different path.
import @firescript/std.  //~ ERROR FS-PARSE-0010 @24
